{"_path":"/maps/_ai/prompt-engineering","_dir":"_ai","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"提示工程 (Prompt Engineering)","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"提示工程-prompt-engineering"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提示工程 (Prompt Engineering)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"dspy声明式提示编程框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DSPy：声明式提示编程框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DSPy 是斯坦福 NLP 团队开源的框架，将提示工程从\"手工调优\"转变为\"编程优化\"。核心抽象包括 Signature（声明输入输出语义）、Module（可组合的计算单元）、Optimizer（自动优化提示和权重）、Teleprompter（少样本示例编译器）。开发者只需描述任务逻辑，DSPy 自动优化提示词、选择示例、微调小模型，在多跳问答等任务上超越手工提示。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/stanfordnlp/dspy","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DSPy GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://dspy.ai/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DSPy 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2310.03714","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DSPy 论文"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"instructor结构化输出解析库"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Instructor：结构化输出解析库"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Instructor 基于 Pydantic 构建，解决 LLM 输出结构化的问题。通过定义数据模型类，自动将 LLM 的文本响应解析为强类型对象，内置重试、验证、流式处理。支持 OpenAI、Anthropic、Gemini 等主流模型，是生产环境中类型安全调用 LLM 的首选方案。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/jxnl/instructor","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Instructor GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://python.useinstructor.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Instructor 文档"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"guidance约束生成控制模板"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Guidance：约束生成控制模板"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Guidance 提供模板语法控制 LLM 的生成过程，支持在生成中强制特定格式（JSON、正则匹配）、动态选择分支、变量插值。通过控制流与生成交错，大幅减少无效输出和后续解析失败，适合需要严格输出格式的场景。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/guidance-ai/guidance","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Guidance GitHub"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"outlines可靠的文本结构化生成"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Outlines：可靠的文本结构化生成"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Outlines 通过预编译正则表达式或 JSON Schema 到高效索引结构，实现完全符合格式的生成。与 Guidance 相比更轻量、性能更高，支持批量生成和多种模型后端，是结构化生成的现代替代方案。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/outlines-dev/outlines","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Outlines GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://dottxt-ai.github.io/outlines/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Outlines 文档"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"工具选型指南"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工具选型指南"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"选择取决于控制粒度：Instructor 适合\"解析已知格式的响应\"，Pydantic 验证确保类型安全；Guidance/Outlines 适合\"强制模型按格式生成\"，从源头约束输出结构。DSPy 则用于系统级优化，自动迭代提示策略。实际项目中常组合使用：Outlines 控制格式，Instructor 验证解析，DSPy 优化整体流程。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/dspy-vs-instructor-pydantic-ai-which-one-right-you-answer-sancare-phdie","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DSPy vs Instructor 对比"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/outlines-dev/outlines/blob/main/benchmarks/benchmark_readme.md","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Outlines vs Guidance 性能对比"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"dspy声明式提示编程框架","depth":2,"text":"DSPy：声明式提示编程框架"},{"id":"instructor结构化输出解析库","depth":2,"text":"Instructor：结构化输出解析库"},{"id":"guidance约束生成控制模板","depth":2,"text":"Guidance：约束生成控制模板"},{"id":"outlines可靠的文本结构化生成","depth":2,"text":"Outlines：可靠的文本结构化生成"},{"id":"工具选型指南","depth":2,"text":"工具选型指南"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:prompt-engineering.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/prompt-engineering.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/prompt-engineering","_extension":"md"}